Enhance PNM support for bitonal images and improve header parsing

- Added support for P4 (bitonal) PNM format in the PNMHeader class, including properties for bitonal detection and bytes per row calculation.
- Updated the _try_parse_header function to handle P4 format and adjusted maxval handling accordingly.
- Implemented raster processing for P4 images in build_partial_jpeg and raster_to_image functions.
- Added unit tests to validate P4 header parsing and raster processing functionality.
